 SOLUTION
 ========

  Ok, here"s the situation....>Sound Familar?<  Anyways, after you have 
read the SG2 novella you are ready to begin.  The first step is to find
the MAIN DEPOT on planet APOGEE.  To do this, enter the tunnels and proceed
straight.  At the next junction, stop, and turn 180 degrees.  You should 
now see the tunnel split.  Now go to your right (you just came from the
left).  Proceed forward.   Keep going!  Next blast open the door.  Stay to 
your left....GO LEFT!  Then about 30 sec later you will be in the 
MAIN DEPOT.  This is where you will recieve your instructions and what 
materials are needed to construct the bomb. (Just like the Novella!)
After your little "chat" proceed back out of the tunnel and onto the 
planet.  Then go refuel.  You do know how to refuel dont ya?!  Well just
find the power lines and fly parallel with them going med speed.  There all
done ready to kill some Egrons?!  Well not yet.  Here"s a quick rundown of
completing the next 25-40% of the game from the begining.....Details, will
follow later on.







