 HINTS & TID BITS
 ================ 

   - All DEPOTS containing items on moons of MILLWAY are at
      position 5502.  ALL ARE IDENTICAL!!!
 
   - You cannot land on MILLWAY.  You will die before you get even
      half way there....So don"t waste your time.  

   - When is tunnel systems, an energy beam or closed door usually
      means there is a depot beyond it, so go for it!

   - Do not fire aimlessly!  You do have limited shots.  Pick carefully.

   - WEAPONS     * Bouning bombs are used primarily against the
                    EGRON projectors on the moons of Millway.
                    Use them wisely.  One is sufficient to knock
                    it out.....Get more bombs on CASTRON.

                 * Homing missiles, use only on moving targets....
                    Great for pirate ships.  Get more missiles
                    at depots on moons of Millway.

                 * Neutron Bomb...Aim at hub of Space Station.

   - Always refuel whenever you have the chance, you never know!
   
   - REFUELING   * Power Lines, the only planets that have these are
                    Apogee & Vista.  Just fly parallel with them at
                    half speed.  You FUEL will be energized first.
                    Then Shields & Lasers....It will take three passes
                    to energize ALL off them...
             
                 * Asteroids, just find them, stop, tractor beam them
                    and just wait.  About two should do the trick.  
                    Fast & easy!  

                 * Volcanoes, kinda hard....Hover high above the opening
                    or you wil get hit by the rocks....Takes awhile!

                 * SUN, Too hard!  You always end up wasting more power
                    then you get....Also dangerous!

    - Save your game OFTEN!  Really, if you wanna solve the game, save
       everytime you accomplish the next goal....Saved me a many times!

    - Check the status of EGRON space station with STATUS REPORT.
       Key "R" - This will also let you know how YOUR BOMB is coming
       along.

    - To build the bomb faster, get at least the first 4 items or so
       and then get the PROFESSOR.  In this way, he will start work on 
       the bomb while you colect the rest of the items.  If you wait to
       get him LAST, then you waste more time!  Just a suggestion....

    - Try to keep at least ONE EGRON Projector base out of commission
       as this halts all work on the space base, which in turn gives 
       YOU MORE time!

    - Tunnel network is in a GIANT CIRCLE....So if you get lost, you
       will end up at sometime back where you were....

